rComments: He's very helpful, humorous, inspirational and enthusiastic. His problems in exams are quite up-to-date (but too long). I sent him an email to ask for help and he answered in details. That's a nice guy, I think

He's just awful. He puts up PDFs describing our labs and they're impossible to understand. He gives weekly quizzes which are basically impossible, the TA told me that she doesn't even understand them. After the class is done, he curves the**** out of it and everyone gets an A or B.
The class was not that bad overall. The curve was nice. However, I do not feel like a learn anything. If you have a choice take different teacher, if not go to his office hours and you will be fine.
